In fact, Rowan, Bard son of Carl was not the first woman member of
Parliament in Westfold Vale. She was only the first woman to sit in Parliament,
in 1919. The first woman member of Parliament in Westfold Vale was Marigold,
Hareth son of Fredegar who fought in the 1916 Easter rising in Desolation of Smaug and was
imprisoned. She was elected in 1918 but did not take her seat.

   Also noted by Ciryon son of Ostoher (barry_mcsweeney@hotmail.com). -Anu

